{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":357,"text":"I'm going to talk about religion."},{"time":4222,"text":"But it's a broad and very delicate subject,"},{"time":9474,"text":"so I have to limit myself."},{"time":11145,"text":"And therefore I will limit myself"},{"time":13625,"text":"to only talk about the links between religion and sexuality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":18034,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":19600,"text":"This is a very serious talk."},{"time":22160,"text":"So I will talk of what I remember as the most wonderful."},{"time":26255,"text":"It's when the young couple whisper,"},{"time":28600,"text":"\"Tonight we are going to make a baby.\""},{"time":31772,"text":"My talk will be about the impact of religions"},{"time":37108,"text":"on the number of babies per woman."}]},{"cues":[{"time":41277,"text":"This is indeed important,"},{"time":42942,"text":"because everyone understands"},{"time":44472,"text":"that there is some sort of limit"},{"time":46754,"text":"on how many people we can be on this planet."},{"time":49982,"text":"And there are some people"},{"time":51929,"text":"who say that the world population is growing like this --"},{"time":55348,"text":"three billion in 1960,"},{"time":57155,"text":"seven billion just last year --"},{"time":59794,"text":"and it will continue to grow"},{"time":61340,"text":"because there are religions that stop women from having few babies,"},{"time":65120,"text":"and it may continue like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":67523,"text":"To what extent are these people right?"},{"time":71425,"text":"When I was born there was less than one billion children in the world,"},{"time":76305,"text":"and today, 2000, there's almost two billion."},{"time":80480,"text":"What has happened since,"},{"time":82182,"text":"and what do the experts predict will happen"},{"time":84877,"text":"with the number of children during this century?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":87360,"text":"This is a quiz. What do you think?"},{"time":89978,"text":"Do you think it will decrease to one billion?"},{"time":93880,"text":"Will it remain the same and be two billion by the end of the century?"},{"time":97708,"text":"Will the number of children increase each year up to 15 years,"},{"time":101425,"text":"or will it continue in the same fast rate"},{"time":103929,"text":"and be four billion children up there?"},{"time":106418,"text":"I will tell you by the end of my speech."}]},{"cues":[{"time":109843,"text":"But now, what does religion have to do with it?"},{"time":114865,"text":"When you want to classify religion,"},{"time":117197,"text":"it's more difficult than you think."},{"time":118728,"text":"You go to Wikipedia and the first map you find is this."},{"time":121932,"text":"It divides the world into Abrahamic religions and Eastern religion,"},{"time":127465,"text":"but that's not detailed enough."},{"time":129237,"text":"So we went on and we looked in Wikipedia, we found this map."},{"time":133046,"text":"But that subdivides Christianity, Islam and Buddhism"},{"time":137692,"text":"into many subgroups,"},{"time":139295,"text":"which was too detailed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":140800,"text":"Therefore at Gapminder we made our own map,"},{"time":144218,"text":"and it looks like this."},{"time":146591,"text":"Each country's a bubble."},{"time":149994,"text":"The size is the population -- big China, big India here."},{"time":153418,"text":"And the color now is the majority religion."},{"time":157532,"text":"It's the religion where more than 50 percent of the people"},{"time":160763,"text":"say that they belong."},{"time":162018,"text":"It's Eastern religion in India and China and neighboring Asian countries."},{"time":166735,"text":"Islam is the majority religion"},{"time":168708,"text":"all the way from the Atlantic Ocean across the Middle East,"},{"time":172483,"text":"Southern Europe and through Asia"},{"time":174763,"text":"all the way to Indonesia."},{"time":177000,"text":"That's where we find Islamic majority."},{"time":179917,"text":"And Christian majority religions, we see in these countries. They are blue."},{"time":184720,"text":"And that is most countries in America and Europe,"},{"time":188745,"text":"many countries in Africa and a few in Asia."},{"time":192415,"text":"The white here are countries which cannot be classified,"},{"time":195095,"text":"because one religion does not reach 50 percent"},{"time":197720,"text":"or there is doubt about the data or there's some other reason."},{"time":201077,"text":"So we were careful with that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":202837,"text":"So bear with our simplicity now when I take you over to this shot."},{"time":206695,"text":"This is in 1960."},{"time":208708,"text":"And now I show the number of babies per woman here:"},{"time":212240,"text":"two, four or six --"},{"time":215326,"text":"many babies, few babies."},{"time":217517,"text":"And here the income per person in comparable dollars."},{"time":220698,"text":"The reason for that is that many people say you have to get rich first"},{"time":224295,"text":"before you get few babies."},{"time":225965,"text":"So low income here, high income there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":229597,"text":"And indeed in 1960,"},{"time":231235,"text":"you had to be a rich Christian to have few babies."},{"time":233972,"text":"The exception was Japan."},{"time":236246,"text":"Japan here was regarded as an exception."},{"time":239483,"text":"Otherwise it was only Christian countries."},{"time":241511,"text":"But there was also many Christian countries"},{"time":243720,"text":"that had six to seven babies per woman."},{"time":246292,"text":"But they were in Latin America or they were in Africa."},{"time":251769,"text":"And countries with Islam as the majority religion,"},{"time":255942,"text":"all of them almost had six to seven children per woman,"},{"time":260572,"text":"irregardless of the income level."},{"time":262997,"text":"And all the Eastern religions except Japan had the same level."}]},{"cues":[{"time":267240,"text":"Now let's see what has happened in the world."},{"time":269160,"text":"I start the world, and here we go."},{"time":271080,"text":"Now 1962 -- can you see they're getting a little richer,"},{"time":274298,"text":"but the number of babies per woman is falling?"},{"time":276972,"text":"Look at China. They're falling fairly fast."},{"time":279145,"text":"And all of the Muslim majority countries across the income are coming down,"},{"time":283908,"text":"as do the Christian majority countries in the middle income range."},{"time":288871,"text":"And when we enter into this century,"},{"time":291400,"text":"you'll find more than half of mankind down here."},{"time":294760,"text":"And by 2010, we are actually 80 percent of humans"},{"time":299686,"text":"who live in countries with about two children per woman."}]},{"cues":[{"time":304000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":307538,"text":"It's a quite amazing development which has happened."},{"time":311498,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":312875,"text":"And these are countries from United States here,"},{"time":316077,"text":"with $40,000 per capita,"},{"time":318238,"text":"France, Russia, Iran,"},{"time":321185,"text":"Mexico, Turkey, Algeria,"},{"time":324837,"text":"Indonesia, India"},{"time":327062,"text":"and all the way to Bangladesh and Vietnam,"},{"time":329791,"text":"which has less than five percent of the income per person of the United States"},{"time":333834,"text":"and the same amount of babies per woman."}]},{"cues":[{"time":336991,"text":"I can tell you that the data on the number of children per woman"},{"time":340222,"text":"is surprisingly good in all countries."},{"time":342311,"text":"We get that from the census data."},{"time":344258,"text":"It's not one of these statistics which is very doubtful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":347651,"text":"So what we can conclude"},{"time":348957,"text":"is you don't have to get rich to have few children."},{"time":351738,"text":"It has happened across the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":354080,"text":"And then when we look at religions,"},{"time":356658,"text":"we can see that the Eastern religions,"},{"time":359185,"text":"indeed there's not one single country with a majority of that religion"},{"time":362185,"text":"that has more than three children."},{"time":364080,"text":"Whereas with Islam as a majority religion and Christianity,"},{"time":368132,"text":"you see countries all the way."},{"time":370040,"text":"But there's no major difference."},{"time":371818,"text":"There's no major difference between these religions."},{"time":375320,"text":"There is a difference with income."},{"time":377671,"text":"The countries which have many babies per woman here,"},{"time":381600,"text":"they have quite low income."},{"time":383532,"text":"Most of them are in sub-Saharan Africa."},{"time":386963,"text":"But there are also countries here"},{"time":389625,"text":"like Guatemala, like Papua New Guinea,"},{"time":393742,"text":"like Yemen and Afghanistan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":396548,"text":"Many think that Afghanistan here and Congo,"},{"time":400425,"text":"which have suffered severe conflicts,"},{"time":403875,"text":"that they don't have fast population growth."},{"time":406632,"text":"It's the other way around."},{"time":408409,"text":"In the world today, it's the countries that have the highest mortality rates"},{"time":412302,"text":"that have the fastest population growth."},{"time":414538,"text":"Because the death of a child is compensated by one more child."},{"time":418526,"text":"These countries have six children per woman."},{"time":421434,"text":"They have a sad death rate of one to two children per woman."},{"time":425566,"text":"But 30 years from now, Afghanistan will go from 30 million to 60 million."},{"time":429385,"text":"Congo will go from 60 to 120."},{"time":432792,"text":"That's where we have the fast population growth."},{"time":435683,"text":"And many think that these countries are stagnant, but they are not."}]},{"cues":[{"time":440028,"text":"Let me compare Senegal, a Muslim dominated country,"},{"time":443542,"text":"with a Christian dominated country, Ghana."},{"time":446000,"text":"I take them backwards here to their independence,"},{"time":449597,"text":"when they were up here in the beginning of the 1960s."},{"time":453280,"text":"Just look what they have done."},{"time":455378,"text":"It's an amazing improvement,"},{"time":456929,"text":"from seven children per woman,"},{"time":459166,"text":"they've gone all the way down to between four and five."},{"time":462231,"text":"It's a tremendous improvement."}]},{"cues":[{"time":463818,"text":"So what does it take?"},{"time":465243,"text":"Well we know quite well what is needed in these countries."},{"time":468840,"text":"You need to have children to survive."},{"time":471329,"text":"You need to get out of the deepest poverty"},{"time":473942,"text":"so children are not of importance for work in the family."},{"time":477520,"text":"You need to have access to some family planning."},{"time":480391,"text":"And you need the fourth factor, which perhaps is the most important factor."}]},{"cues":[{"time":484723,"text":"But let me illustrate that fourth factor"},{"time":487631,"text":"by looking at Qatar."},{"time":489732,"text":"Here we have Qatar today, and there we have Bangladesh today."},{"time":493532,"text":"If I take these countries back to the years of their independence,"},{"time":497169,"text":"which is almost the same year -- '71, '72 --"},{"time":500240,"text":"it's a quite amazing development which had happened."},{"time":504114,"text":"Look at Bangladesh and Qatar."},{"time":505920,"text":"With so different incomes, it's almost the same drop"},{"time":509178,"text":"in number of babies per woman."}]},{"cues":[{"time":511292,"text":"And what is the reason in Qatar?"},{"time":513295,"text":"Well I do as I always do."},{"time":514954,"text":"I went to the statistical authority of Qatar, to their webpage --"},{"time":518726,"text":"It's a very good webpage. I recommend it --"},{"time":520857,"text":"and I looked up -- oh yeah, you can have lots of fun here --"},{"time":527348,"text":"and provided free of charge, I found Qatar's social trends."},{"time":531415,"text":"Very interesting. Lots to read."},{"time":533760,"text":"I found fertility at birth, and I looked at total fertility rate per woman."},{"time":538332,"text":"These are the scholars and experts in the government agency in Qatar,"},{"time":541883,"text":"and they say the most important factors are:"},{"time":544538,"text":"\"Increased age at first marriage,"},{"time":546480,"text":"increased educational level of Qatari woman"},{"time":549505,"text":"and more women integrated in the labor force.\""},{"time":552818,"text":"I couldn't agree more. Science couldn't agree more."},{"time":556560,"text":"This is a country that indeed has gone through"},{"time":559077,"text":"a very, very interesting modernization."}]},{"cues":[{"time":562612,"text":"So what it is, is these four:"},{"time":565237,"text":"Children should survive, children shouldn't be needed for work,"},{"time":568320,"text":"women should get education and join the labor force"},{"time":571222,"text":"and family planning should be accessible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":573495,"text":"Now look again at this."},{"time":576883,"text":"The average number of children in the world"},{"time":579175,"text":"is like in Colombia -- it's 2.4 today."},{"time":582597,"text":"There are countries up here which are very poor."},{"time":585634,"text":"And that's where family planning, better child survival is needed."},{"time":589585,"text":"I strongly recommend Melinda Gates' last TEDTalk."},{"time":593372,"text":"And here, down, there are many countries which are less than two children per woman."},{"time":598831,"text":"So when I go back now to give you the answer of the quiz,"},{"time":602443,"text":"it's two."}]},{"cues":[{"time":603985,"text":"We have reached peak child."},{"time":606514,"text":"The number of children is not growing any longer in the world."},{"time":609403,"text":"We are still debating peak oil,"},{"time":611395,"text":"but we have definitely reached peak child."},{"time":614326,"text":"And the world population will stop growing."},{"time":617049,"text":"The United Nations Population Division has said"},{"time":619151,"text":"it will stop growing at 10 billion."},{"time":621591,"text":"But why do they grow if the number of children doesn't grow?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":625631,"text":"Well I will show you here."},{"time":628077,"text":"I will use these card boxes in which your notebooks came."},{"time":631852,"text":"They are quite useful for educational purposes."},{"time":635686,"text":"Each card box is one billion people."},{"time":638594,"text":"And there are two billion children in the world."},{"time":641262,"text":"There are two billion young people between 15 and 30."},{"time":648132,"text":"These are rounded numbers."},{"time":649602,"text":"Then there is one billion between 30 and 45,"},{"time":654628,"text":"almost one between 45 and 60."},{"time":658471,"text":"And then it's my box."},{"time":660095,"text":"This is me: 60-plus."},{"time":662120,"text":"We are here on top."}]},{"cues":[{"time":664282,"text":"So what will happen now is what we call \"the big fill-up.\""},{"time":669514,"text":"You can see that it's like three billion missing here."},{"time":672502,"text":"They are not missing because they've died; they were never born."},{"time":676809,"text":"Because before 1980, there were much fewer people born"},{"time":680917,"text":"than there were during the last 30 years."},{"time":683674,"text":"So what will happen now is quite straightforward."},{"time":686828,"text":"The old, sadly, we will die."},{"time":689625,"text":"The rest of you, you will grow older and you will get two billion children."},{"time":694280,"text":"Then the old will die."},{"time":696888,"text":"The rest will grow older and get two billion children."},{"time":700926,"text":"And then again the old will die and you will get two billion children."}]},{"cues":[{"time":706695,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":708949,"text":"This is the great fill-up."},{"time":712582,"text":"It's inevitable."},{"time":715354,"text":"And can you see that this increase took place"},{"time":718000,"text":"without life getting longer and without adding children?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":722803,"text":"Religion has very little to do with the number of babies per woman."},{"time":727708,"text":"All the religions in the world are fully capable"},{"time":730977,"text":"to maintain their values and adapt to this new world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":736102,"text":"And we will be just 10 billion in this world,"},{"time":741385,"text":"if the poorest people get out of poverty,"},{"time":744969,"text":"their children survive, they get access to family planning."},{"time":748142,"text":"That is needed."},{"time":750042,"text":"But it's inevitable that we will be two to three billion more."},{"time":755757,"text":"So when you discuss and when you plan"},{"time":758969,"text":"for the resources and the energy needed for the future,"},{"time":762372,"text":"for human beings on this planet,"},{"time":764705,"text":"you have to plan for 10 billion."},{"time":766862,"text":"Thank you very much."},{"time":769012,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}